)%20in%20the%20first%20match%20of%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League.%20On%20their%20home%20turf%20and%20in%20front%20of%20their%20crowd%2C%20the%20defending%20champions%20fell%20short%20and%20surrendered%20to%20an%20emphatic%207-wicket%20defeat%20at%20the%20iconic%20Eden%20Gardens.%20After%20being%20put%20to%20bat%20and%20struggling%20against%20the%20early%20blitz%20of%20Josh%20Hazlewood%2C%20Rahane%20and%20Sunil%20Narine%20upped%20the%20ante%20by%20resorting%20to%20a%20fearless%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20turned%20the%20tides%20by%20attacking%20relentlessly%20and%20lifted%20the%20Knights%20to%20107%2F1%20in%209.5%20overs.%20Against%20the%20run%20of%20play%2C%20RCB%20found%20the%20breakthrough%20with%20Rasikh%20Salam%20punching%20Narine's%20(44)%20return%20ticket%20to%20the%20dressing%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20floodgates%20blew%20wide%20open%2C%20and%20Krunal%20Pandya%20capitalised%20on%20the%20opportunity.%20He%20struck%20twice%20in%20quick%20succession%20to%20leave%20KKR%20tattering%20at%20145%2F5.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20moment%20for%20Rahane%20when%20he%20felt%20the%20momentum%20turn%20its%20face%20away%20from%20the%20defending%20champions%2C%20which%20left%20them%20incapable%20of%20breaching%20the%20200-run%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%20we%20were%20going%20well%20till%20the%2013th%20over%2C%20but%202-3%20wickets%20changed%20the%20momentum.%20Batters%20that%20followed%20tried%20their%20best%2C%20but%20it%20didn't%20work%20out.%20When%20Venky%20and%20I%20were%20batting%2C%20we%20discussed%20that%20200-210%20was%20achievable%2C%20but%20those%20wickets%20changed%20the%20momentum%2C%26quot%3B%20Rahane%20said%20in%20the%20post-match%20presentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20little%20bit%20of%20dew%20was%20there%2C%20but%20they%20had%20a%20very%20good%20powerplay%20with%20the%20bat.%20It%20(total)%20was%20under%20par.%20We%20were%20looking%20for%20200-plus%20(score).%20We%20don't%20want%20to%20think%20too%20much%20about%20this%20game%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20just%20try%20and%20get%20better%20in%20certain%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20KKR%20limped%20to%20174%2F8%2C%20the%20explosive%20opening%20duo%20of%20Philip%20Salt%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20set%20the%20Eden%20Gardens%20ablaze%20with%20a%20searing%20display%20with%20the%20bat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spectators%20were%20left%20mesmerised%20as%20RCB%20chants%20took%20over%20the%20cricketing%20hub%20of%20Kolkata.%20They%20raised%20a%2095-run%20opening%20stand%20to%20take%20the%20game%20out%20of%20KKR's%20grasp%20and%20cruise%20to%20a%207-wicket%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742696520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fm5i7v5eg_rahane-ajinkya-bcci_625x300_23_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fnot-virat-kohli-kkr-captain-ajinkya-rahane-explains-what-changed-momentum-in-rcbs-favour-7987301%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20KKR%20limped%20to%20174%2F8%2C%20the%20explosive%20opening%20duo%20of%20Philip%20Salt%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20set%20the%20Eden%20Gardens%20ablaze%20with%20a%20searing%20display%20with%20the%20bat.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Are%20Nigerians%20abroad%20widening%20the%20class%20divide%20back%20home%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742696471000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F2946%2Flive%2Faf8d0f40-072f-11f0-97d3-37df2b293ed1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcvg1p5ek72vo%232%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Some%20locals%20find%20they%20cannot%20compete%20with%20those