t%20a%20few%20months.%20We%20were%20at%20a%20local%20band%20concert%20in%20a%20small%20venue%2C%20and%20the%20corndog%20in%20question%20was%20at%20the%20restaurant%20next%20door.%20So%2C%20I%20told%20him%20maybe%20later%20on%20the%20food%20and%20drink.%20He%20told%20me%20to%20find%20him%20whenever%20I%20wanted%20to%20collect%20my%20thank%20you%2C%20that%20he%20would%20be%20ready.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20parted%20ways%2C%20me%20back%20to%20my%20group%20of%20friends%20and%20he%20to%20his.%20I%20thought%20that%20would%20be%20the%20end%20of%20things%2C%20but%20when%20I%20went%20to%20leave%20after%20the%20show%2C%20he%20saw%20me%20and%20asked%20if%20I%20was%20ready%20for%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrauma-dump-dates-sobriety-saved-dating-life-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20drink%20he%20owed%20me%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20I%20don't%20remember%20what%20words%20I%20stumbled%20through%2C%20some%20version%20of%20%26quot%3Byou%20don't%20have%20to%20do%20that%2C%20really.%26quot%3B%20But%20a%20few%20minutes%20after%20I%20slid%20onto%20a%20bar%20stool%20next%20door%2C%20there%20he%20was%20next%20to%20me.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20sat%20side-by-side%20at%20the%20bar%2C%20ordered%20beers%20and%20corndogs%20as%20promised%2C%20and%20started%20a%20conversation%20that%20lasted%20until%20the%20wee%20hours%20of%20the%20night.%20People%20came%20and%20went%2C%20the%20music%20pulsed%20around%20us%2C%20but%20nothing%20interrupted%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmet-husband-english-conversation-class-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecomfortable%20intimacy%20building%20between%20us%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e7a8bba8-10d5-4b0a-a56e-6a4fbee14162%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20the%20start%20of%20an%20endless%20conversation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20didn't%20matter%20what%20we%20talked%20about%20(and%20our%20topics%20covered%20the%20gamut%20from%20banal%20details%20to%20deeper%20thoughts)%3B%20the%20conversation%20was%20easy.%20One%20topic%20was%20that%20he%20was%20sure%20he%20would%20be%20a%20lifelong%20bachelor%20but%20wished%20that%20wasn't%20the%20truth.%20His%20ex-girlfriend%20was%20at%20the%20show%2C%20and%20it%20made%20him%20think%20perhaps%20he'd%20made%20a%20mistake%20with%20their%20break-up.%20I%20told%20him%20that%20I%20thought%20he%20was%20too%20caught%20up%20on%20the%20wrong%20thing%2C%20and%20I%20was%20sure%20he'd%20find%20someone%20if%20he%20wanted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20our%20conversation%20stretched%20into%20the%20night%2C%20we%20discovered%20something%20surprising%20%E2%80%94%20we%20weren't%20strangers%20after%20all.%20One%20of%20my%20good%20friends%20had%20been%20cutting%20his%20hair%20for%20nearly%20a%20decade.%20I%20knew%20his%20last%20roommate.%20Our%20social%20circles%20overlapped%20in%20a%20dozen%20ways%2C%20yet%20somehow%2C%20we%20had%20never%20really%20met.%20Or%20so%20I%20thought.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20where%20is%20your%20curly-haired%20boyfriend%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20turned%20out%20this%20wasn't%20our%20first%20meeting.%20We%20had%20actually%20met%20twice%20before%2C%20also%20at%20concerts.%20He%20remembered.%20I%20didn't.%20And%20as%20I%20explained%20that%20my%20boyfriend%20and%20I%20had%20recently%20broken%20up%2C%20I%20watched%20his%20expression%20shift.%20I%20could%20see%20the%20exact%20moment%20he%20realized%20he%20wished%20he%20hadn't%20mentioned%20his%20ex-girlfriend%20earlier%20in%20our%20conversation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2235854f5b-cff8-4b52-96be-1d8dfe33d135%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20never%20doubted%20his%20interest%20in%20me%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20night%20ended%2C%20he%20asked%20for%20my%20number%20and%20then%20texted%20me%20before%20I%20made%20the%20five-minute%20ride%20home.%20He%20wanted%20me%20to%20know%2C%20without%20a%20doubt%2C%20that%20he%20was%20interested%20in%20seeing%20me%20again%20whenever%20I%20was%20ready.%20We%20went%20on%20our%20first%20date%20two%20days%20later%20and%20never%20stopped%20dating.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENearly%20two%20decades%2C%20three%20cities%2C%20three%20children%2C%20and%20plenty%20of%20life's%20ups%20and%20downs%20later%2C%20we're%20still%20building%20on%20that%20same%20connection%20we%20felt%20that%20night.%20Throughout%20it%20all%2C%20my%20husband%20has%20been%20steady%20and%20unwavering.%20In%20our%20early%20dating%20days%2C%20my%20friends%20used%20to%20wish%20he%20had%20a%20sibling%3B%20these%20days%2C%20they%20jokingly%20call%20us%20%26quot%3Brelationship%20goals.%26quot%3B%20And%20I%20couldn't%20agree%20more.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20loose%20zipper%20and%20a%20real-life%20meet-cute%20led%20me%20to%20a%20life%20more%20perfect%20than%20I%20could%20have%20imagined.%20It%20turns%20out%20that%20sometimes%20love%20is%20like%20the%20movies%20%E2%80%94%20just%20with%20better%20snacks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwardrobe-mishap-couple-met-together-decades-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742684162000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67db2633b8b41a9673fb2503%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwardrobe-mishap-couple-met-together-decades-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20didn't%20know%20him%20but%20I%20always%20prefer%20brutal%20honesty.%20He%20bought%20me%20a%20beer%20and%20now%20we%20have%20three%20kids%20together%20after%20almost%20two%20decades%20in%20love.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Tiffany%20Nieslanik)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%