h%20was%20not%20found%20on%20site%20as%20I%20had%20seen%20it.%20It%20was%20this%20which%20prompted%20me%20to%20observe%20that%20this%20clearly%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20frame%20and%20malign%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Varma%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20a%20video%20shared%20by%20the%20police%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20portions%20of%20the%20documents%20including%20names%20have%20been%20redacted%20to%20maintain%20confidentiality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsee-delhi-high-court-chief-justice-full-report-documents-on-judge-cash-row-7987189%5C%22%3EDelhi%20High%20Court%20Chief%20Justice's%20Full%20Report%2C%20Documents%20On%20Judge%20Cash%20Row%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20report%20submitted%20to%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%2C%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20Chief%20Justice%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20He%20%5BJustice%20Varma%5D%20also%20informed%20me%20that%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20he%20was%20in%20Bhopal%20and%20got%20the%20information%20from%20his%20daughter.%20Justice%20Verma%20further%20told%20me%20that%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20black%20burnt%20material%20(soot)%20is%20lying%20in%20the%20room.%20I%20thereafter%20showed%20him%20the%20photographs%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fshorts%2Fvideo-of-burnt-currency-notes-shared-by-delhi-police-chief-in-judge-cash-row-917066%5C%22%3Evideo%20on%20my%20WhatsApp%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20were%20shared%20with%20me%20by%20the%20Commissioner%20of%20Police.%20He%20%5BJustice%20Varma%5D%20then%20expressed%20some%20apprehension%20about%20some%20conspiracy%20against%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20documents%20uploaded%20on%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20website%20show%20that%20on%20March%2021%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20shared%20three%20questions%20with%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20Chief%20Justice%20that%20can%20be%20asked%20to%20Justice%20Varma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20questions%20were%3A%20how%20does%20he%20account%20for%20the%20presence%20of%20money%2Fcash%20in%20the%20room%20located%20in%20his%20premises%3F%20Explain%20the%20source%20of%20money%2Fcash%20which%20was%20found%20in%20the%20said%20room.%20Who%20is%20the%20person%20who%20had%20removed%20the%20burnt%20money%2Fcash%20from%20the%20room%20in%20the%20morning%20of%20March%2015%2C%202025%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20sought%20details%20of%20the%20official%20staff%20of%20the%20high%20court%20Registry%2C%20the%20personal%20security%20officers%20and%20the%20security%20guards%20who%20were%20posted%20at%20Justice%20Varma's%20house%20in%20the%20last%20six%20months.%20He%20suggested%20contacting%20the%20mobile%20service%20provider(s)%20for%20giving%20call%20record%20details%20of%20the%20official%20or%20other%20mobile%20phone%20number(s)%20of%20Justice%20Varma%20for%20the%20last%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Ff4aj2l1_delhi-high-court-judge-justice-yashwant-varma_625x300_21_March_25.jpeg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Ch%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJustice%20Yashwant%20Varma%20may%20be%20requested%20to%20not%20dispose%20of%20his%20mobile%20phone(s)%20or%20delete%20or%20modify%20any%20conversation%2C%20messages%20or%20data%20from%20his%20mobile%20phone(s).%20The%20reply%20submitted%20by%20Justice%20Yashwant%20Varma%2C%20along%20with%20your%20comments%2C%20may%20be%20furnished%20to%20me%20immediately%20for%20further%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20said%20in%20a%20written%20communication%20to%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20Chief%20Justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20High%20Court%20Chief%20Justice%20DK%20Upadhyaya%20asked%20these%20three%20and%20other%20questions%20to%20Justice%20Varma%2C%20with%20a%20request%20to%20respond%20by%20Saturday%20midnight%20since%20%26quot%3Bthe%20reported%20incident%20is%20very%20disturbing%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJustice%20Yashwant%20Varma's%20Response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Varma%20said%20the%20fire%20broke%20out%20in%20the%20storeroom%20near%20the%20staff%20quarters%20of%20his%20official%20residence%20on%20the%20intervening%20night%20of%2014-15%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20room%20was%20generally%20utilised%20by%20all%20and%20sundry%20to%20store%20articles%20such%20as%20unused%20furniture%2C%20bottles%2C%20crockery%2C%20mattresses%2C%20used%20carpets%2C%20old%20speakers%2C%20garden%20implements%20as%20well%20as%20CPWD%20material.%20This%20room%20is%20unlocked%20and%20accessible%20both%20from%20the%20official%20front%20gate%20as%20well%20as%20the%20backdoor%20of%20the%20staff%20quarters.%20It%20is%20disconnected%20from%20the%20main%20residence%20and%20is%20surely%20not%20a%20room%20in%20my%20house%20as%20has%20been%20portrayed%20and%20suggested%20in%20the%20article%20which%20appeared%20in%20the%20Times%20of%20India%20and%20certain%20other%20news%20reports.%20On%20that%20date%2C%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20were%20not%20in%20Delhi%20and%20travelling%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20it%20was%20only%20my%20daughter%20and%20aged%20mother%20who%20were%20at%20home.%20I%20returned%20to%20Delhi%20only%20on%20the%20evening%20of%2015%20March%20from%20Bhopal%20travelling%20on%20an%20IndiGo%20flight%20with%20my%20wife%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Varma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%2C%20since%20that%20fateful%20night%2C%20been%20continuously%20trying%20to%20find%20an%20explanation%20for%20the%20allegations%20which%20are%20being%20levelled%20and%20with%20us%20being%20required%20to%20prove%20an%20allegation%20which%20is%20premised%20on%20cash%20being%20discovered%20and%20the%20same%20presumed%20to%20belong%20to%20me%20or%20my%20family%20members.%20That%20presumption%20requires%20me%20to%20not%20only%20furnish%20an%20explanation%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20existence%20of%20an%20article%20allegedly%20present%20in%20a%20commonly%20used%20outhouse%20and%20general%20storeroom%20which%20was%20freely%20accessible%20but%20also%20requires%20me%20to%20'account'%20for%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20takes%20me%20to%20the%20video%20clip%20which%20has%20been%20shared%20with%20me.%20Assuming%20without%20admitting%20that%20the%20video%20was%20taken%20immediately%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20incident%20at%20the%20site%2C%20none%20of%20it%20appears%20to%20have%20been%20recovered%20or%20seized.%20The%20second%20aspect%20which%20I%20need%20to%20underscore%20is%20that%20none%20of%20the%20staff%20was%20shown%20any%20remnants%20of%20cash%20or%20currency%20that%20may%20have%20been%20present%20on%20site.%20I%20have%20made%20my%20own%20enquiries%20from%20the%20staff%20present%20who%20have%20also%20stated%20that%20there%20was%20no%20'removal'%20of%20currency%20which%20was%20allegedly%20found%20at%20the%20site%20or%20removed%20from%20the%20premises.%20The%20only%20thing%20which%20was%20cleared%20was%20debris%20and%20what%20they%20considered%20to%20be%20salvageable.%20That%20is%20still%20present%20in%20the%20house%20and%20can%20be%20seen%20kept%20apart%20in%20one%20part%20of%20the%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20baffles%20me%20is%20the%20complete%20absence%20of%20any%20sacks%20of%20allegedly%20burnt%20currency%20which%20were%20ever%20recovered%20or%20seized.%20We%20categorically%20assert%20that%20neither%20my%20daughter%2C%20PS%20%5Bprivate%20secretary%5D%20nor%20household%20staff%20were%20shown%20these%20so-called%20sacks%20of%20burnt%20currency.%20I%20stand%20by%20my%20consistent%20position%20that%20when%20they%20accessed%20the%20storeroom%2C%20there%20was%20no%20currency%2C%20burnt%20or%20otherwise%2C%20which%20could%20be%20seen.%20I%20request%20you%20to%20bear%20in%20mind%20that%20the%20storeroom%20is%20removed%20from%20my%20residence%20and%20is%20used%20as%20a%20general%20dump%20room%20for%20disused%20articles%20and%20other%20sundry%20household%20articles.%20I%20wonder%20who%20would%20countenance%20an%20allegation%20that%20currency%20would%20be%20kept%20in%20a%20storeroom%20in%20a%20corner%20of%20the%20house%20and%20which%20is%20freely%20accessible%20from%20amongst%20others%20the%20back%20wicker%20gate%20also.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20beseech%20you%20to%20also%20bear%20in%20consideration%20that%20no%20currency%20was%20recovered%20from%20the%20premises%20that%20we%20actually%20occupy%20and%20use%20as%20a%20family.%20That%20part%20of%20the%20premises%20is%20as%20indicated%20above%20removed%20from%20the%20living%20quarters.%20It%20is%20in%20the%20aforesaid%20background%20that%20I%20urge%20you%20to%20absolve%20me%20of%20these%20unfounded%20and%20baseless%20allegations.%20In%20the%20life%20of%20a%20judge%2C%20nothing%20matters%20more%20than%20reputation%20and%20character.%20That%20has%20been%20severely%20tarnished%20and%20irreparably%20damaged.%20The%20baseless%20allegations%20that%20have%20been%20levelled%20against%20me%20have%20proceeded%20on%20mere%20innuendos%20and%20an%20unproven%20assumption%20that%20the%20cash%20allegedly%20seen%20and%20found%20belonged%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Varma%20said%20in%20his%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20full%20response%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsee-delhi-high-court-chief-justice-full-report-documents-on-judge-cash-row-7987189%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20lawyer%20Harish%20Salve%2C%20who%20calls%20himself%20a%20%26quot%3Btrenchant%20critic%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20collegium%20system%2C%20told%20NDTV%20on%20Friday%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20equipped%26quot%3B%20to%20deal%20with%20cases%20like%20the%20alleged%20recovery%20of%20a%20huge%20pile%20of%20cash%20at%20the%20home%20of%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Salve%20alleged%20the%20Delhi%20fire%20chief%20has%20said%20there%20was%20no%20recovery%20of%20cash%20from%20the%20judge's%20bungalow%2C%20giving%20rise%20to%20an%20%26quot%3Bodd%20and%20murky%26quot%3B%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20website%20shows%20Justice%20Varma%20enrolled%20as%20an%20advocate%20in%20August%201992.%20He%20was%20appointed%20additional%20judge%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20in%20October%202014.%20He%20took%20oath%20as%20a%20permanent%20judge%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20in%20February%202016%2C%20before%20being%20appointed%20a%20judge%20of%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20in%20October%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20currently%20heading%20a%20division%20bench%2C%20dealing%20with%20cases%20of%20sales%20tax%2C%20goods%20and%20services%20tax%2C%20company%20appeals%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20to%20transfer%20Justice%20Varma%20to%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20was%20also%20unrelated%20to%20the%20inquiry%20into%20the%20alleged%20cash%20stash%20row%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20on%20Friday.%20It%20said%20the%20in-house%20investigation%20was%20being%20done%20as%20per%20the%20procedure%20prescribed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20and%20the%20transfer%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20investigation.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20flagged%20%26quot%3Bmisinformation%20and%20rumours%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20reasons%20why%20Justice%20Varma's%20transfer%20to%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20was%20linked%20to%20the%20alleged%20cash%20recovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742672760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fpmbc4k0o_delhi-judge_625x300_23_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-makes-report-on-judge-cash-row-public-includes-pics-videos-7987105%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20report%20submitted%20by%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20High%20Court%20of%20Delhi%20into%20alleged%20finding%20of%20a%20cash%20stash%20at%20the%20house%20of%20high%20court%20judge%20Justice%20Yashwant%20Varma%20has%20been%20uploaded%20on%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20website.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-makes-report-on-judge-cash-row-public-includes-pics-videos-7987105%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BPreposterous%2C%20Incredible%2C%20Incredulous%26quot%3B%3A%20Judge%20On%20Cash%20Recovery%20Claims%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStrongly%20denying%20that%20he%20or%20his%20family%20had%20kept%20any%20cash%20in%20the%20storeroom%20from%20which%20the%20burnt%20remains%20of%20several%20wads%20of%20notes%20were%20allegedly%20recovered%2C%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20Justice%20Yashwant%20Varma%20has%20said%20the%20room%20is%20disconnected%20from%20his%20main%20residence%20and%20is%20accessible%20to%2C%20and%20used%20by%2C%20several%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20lengthy%20response%20to%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20Chief%20Justice%20Devendra%20Kumar%20Upadhyay%20on%20the%20alleged%20recovery%20of%20cash%2C%20Justice%20Varma%20said%20a%20fire%20broke%20out%20in%20the%20storeroom%20situated%20near%20the%20staff%20quarters%20of%20his%20official%20residence%20in%20Delhi%20late%20on%20the%20night%20of%20March%2014%2C%20which%20was%20Holi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20room%20was%20generally%20utilised%20by%20all%20and%20sundry%20to%20store%20articles%20such%20as%20unused%20furniture%2C%20bottles%2C%20crockery%2C%20mattresses%2C%20used%20carpets%2C%20old%20speakers%2C%20garden%20implements%20as%20well%20as%20CPWD%20(Central%20Public%20Works%20Department)%20material.%20This%20room%20is%20unlocked%20and%20accessible%20both%20from%20the%20official%20front%20gate%20as%20well%20as%20the%20backdoor%20of%20the%20staff%20quarters.%20It%20is%20disconnected%20from%20the%20main%20residence%20and%20is%20surely%20not%20a%20room%20in%20my%20house%20as%20has%20been%20portrayed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Varma%20said%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20were%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20that%20day%20and%20only%20his%20daughter%20and%20aged%20mother%20were%20home.%20He%20said%20he%20returned%20to%20Delhi%20with%20his%20wife%20on%20March%2015%20on%20an%20IndiGo%20flight%20from%20Bhopal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20fire%20broke%20out%20around%20midnight%2C%20the%20fire%20service%20was%20alerted%20by%20my%20daughter%20and%20my%20private%20secretary%20and%20whose%20calls%20would%20be%20duly%20recorded%20(sic).%20During%20the%20exercise%20to%20douse%20the%20fire%2C%20all%20staff%20and%20the%20members%20of%20my%20household%20were%20asked%20to%20move%20away%20from%20the%20scene%20of%20the%20incident%20in%20view%20of%20safety%20concerns.%20After%20the%20fire%20was%20doused%20and%20when%20they%20went%20back%20to%20the%20scene%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20they%20saw%20no%20cash%20or%20currency%20on%20site%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20state%20unequivocally%20that%20no%20cash%20was%20ever%20placed%20in%20that%20storeroom%20either%20by%20me%20or%20any%20of%20my%20family%20members%20and%20strongly%20denounce%20the%20suggestion%20that%20the%20alleged%20cash%20belonged%20to%20us.%20The%20very%20idea%20or%20suggestion%20that%20this%20cash%20was%20kept%20or%20stored%20by%20us%20is%20totally%20preposterous.%20The%20suggestion%20that%20one%20would%20store%20cash%20in%20an%20open%2C%20freely%20accessible%20and%20commonly%20used%20storeroom%20near%20the%20staff%20quarters%20or%20in%20an%20outhouse%20verges%20on%20the%20incredible%20and%20incredulous%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20room%2C%20the%20judge%20said%2C%20is%20completely%20dissociated%20from%20his%20and%20his%20family's%20living%20areas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETimeline%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Varma%20said%20he%20was%20told%20about%20the%20exact%20nature%20of%20the%20incident%20after%20he%20returned%20to%20Delhi.%20%26quot%3BI%20vividly%20recollect%20your%20(Justice%20Upadhyay's)%20first%20phone%20call%20to%20me%20on%20that%20evening%20when%20you%20apprised%20me%20of%20having%20received%20information%20of%20an%20incident%20of%20arson%20at%20my%20residence.%20I%20expressed%20shock%20and%20complete%20disbelief%20since%20till%20that%20time%20I%20was%20led%20to%20believe%20that%20it%20was%20merely%20a%20fire%20caused%20by%20a%20short%20circuit.%20I%20recall%20my%20apprising%20you%20of%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20premises%20and%20the%20articles%20which%20are%20usually%20put%20away%20for%20storage%20in%20that%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Varma%20said%20Justice%20Upadhya%20had%20requested%20for%20the%20PPS%20(principal%20private%20secretary)%20to%20be%20allowed%20to%20visit%20the%20site%20and%20he%20had%20agreed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20PPS%20arrived%20later%20that%20night%20and%20when%20I%2C%20my%20PS%20(private%20secretary)%20along%20with%20the%20PPS%20inspected%20the%20gutted%20room%2C%20no%20currency%20was%20either%20found%20nor%20was%20any%20cash%20in%20any%20state%20seen%20present%20on%20site.%20This%20also%20stands%20corroborated%20from%20the%20report%20which%20has%20been%20provided%20to%20me.%20Post%20that%20inspection%20and%20on%20your%20instructions%2C%20the%20gutted%20room%20remains%20in%20that%20state%20even%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20emphasised.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Conspiracy'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20photos%20and%20videos%20of%20cash%20at%20the%20storeroom%20-%20some%20of%20which%20were%20also%20uploaded%20on%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20website%20on%20Saturday%20-%20Justice%20Varma%20said%20he%20met%20Justice%20Upadhyay%20before%20the%20court%20commenced%20the%20next%20day%20(March%2016)%20and%20was%20shown%20the%20recordings%20which%20were%20shared%20by%20the%20Commissioner%20of%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20totally%20shocked%20to%20see%20the%20contents%20of%20the%20video%20since%20that%20depicted%20something%20which%20was%20not%20found%20on%20site%20as%20I%20had%20seen%20it.%20It%20was%20this%20which%20prompted%20me%20to%20observe%20that%20this%20clearly%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20frame%20and%20malign%20me.%20It%20also%20lends%20credence%20to%20my%20firm%20belief%20that%20the%20entire%20incident%20is%20part%20of%20a%20sequence%20of%20events%20which%20occurred%20in%20the%20recent%20past%20including%20the%20unfounded%20allegations%20that%20circulated%20on%20social%20media%20in%20December%202024%20%5Bwhich%20too%20I%20had%20apprised%20you%20about%20during%20the%20course%20of%20our%20meeting%5D%20and%20your%20first%20reaction%20of%20the%20incident%20being%20that%20of%20arson%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Varma%20wrote%20in%20his%20reply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20the%20lack%20of%20knowledge%20or%20connection%20with%20the%20purported%20discovery%20of%20currency%20is%20what%20prompted%20my%20reaction%20in%20our%20first%20interaction%20in%20respect%20of%20this%20episode%20and%20when%20I%20had%20alluded%20to%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20frame%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReiterating%20that%20neither%20he%20nor%20his%20family%20members%20had%20kept%20money%20in%20the%20storeroom%2C%20Justice%20Varma%20said%20their%20cash%20withdrawals%20are%20documented%20and%20%26quot%3Balways%20through%20regular%20banking%20channels%2C%20the%20use%20of%20UPI%20applications%20and%20cards%26quot%3B.%20He%20asserted%20that%20no%20one%20from%20his%20house%20ever%20reported%20seeing%20any%20currency%20in%20burnt%20form%20in%20the%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20this%20gets%20further%20corroborated%20from%20there%20being%20no%20cash%20or%20currency%20which%20we%20saw%20when%3Cbr%3E%5Cnthe%20site%20was%20restored%20to%20us%20after%20the%20fire%20personnel%20and%20the%20police%20had%20left%20the%20scene%20quite%20apart%20from%20we%20being%20not%20apprised%20of%20any%20recovery%20or%20seizure%20which%20was%20made%20on%20the%20spot%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20High%20Court%20judge%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'No%20One%20Was%20Shown%20Cash'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20takes%20me%20to%20the%20video%20clip%20which%20has%20been%20shared%20with%20me.%20Assuming%20without%20admitting%20that%20the%20video%20was%20taken%20immediately%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20incident%20at%20the%20site%2C%20none%20of%20it%20appears%20to%20have%20been%20recovered%20or%20seized.%20The%20second%20aspect%20which%20I%20need%20to%20underscore%20is%20that%20none%20of%20the%20staff%20was%20shown%20any%20remnants%20of%20cash%20or%20currency%20that%20may%20have%20been%20present%20on%20site%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20wrote%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20staff%20have%20said%20there%20was%20no%20'removal'%20of%20currency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20only%20thing%20which%20was%20cleared%20was%20debris%20and%20what%20they%20considered%20to%20be%20salvageable.%20That%20is%20still%20present%20in%20the%20house%20and%20can%20be%20seen%20kept%20apart%20in%20one%20part%20of%20the%20residence.%20What%20baffles%20me%20is%20the%20complete%20absence%20of%20any%20sacks%20of%20allegedly%20burnt%20currency%20which%20were%20ever%20recovered%20or%20seized.%20We%20categorically%20assert%20that%20neither%20my%20daughter%2C%20PS%20nor%20household%20staff%20were%20shown%20these%20so-called%20sacks%20of%20burnt%20currency.%20I%20stand%20by%20my%20consistent%20position%20that%20when%20they%20accessed%20the%20storeroom%2C%20there%20was%20no%20currency%2C%20burnt%20or%20otherwise%2C%20which%20could%20be%20seen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReputation%2C%20Character%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUrging%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20Chief%20Justice%20too%20absolve%20him%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bunfounded%20and%20baseless%3Cbr%3E%5Cnallegations%26quot%3B%2C%20Justice%20Varma%20said%20nothing%20matters%20more%20in%20the%20life%20of%20a%20judge%20than%20reputation%20and%20character.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20has%20been%20severely%20tarnished%20and%20irreparably%20damaged.%20The%20baseless%20allegations%20that%20have%20been%20levelled%20against%20me%20have%20proceeded%20on%20mere%20innuendos%20and%20an%20unproven%20assumption%20that%20the%20cash%20allegedly%20seen%20and%20found%20belonged%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20incident%20has%20scarred%20my%20reputation%20built%20over%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20as%20a%20judge%20of%20a%20High%20Court%2C%20and%20it%20has%20left%20me%20with%20no%20means%20to%20defend%20myself.%20I%20would%20also%20beseech%20you%20to%20bear%20in%20consideration%20that%20in%20all%20my%20years%20as%20a%20judge%20of%20a%20High%20Court%2C%20no%20such%20allegation%20had%20ever%20been%20made%20in%20the%20past%20nor%20any%20doubt%20cast%20on%20my%20integrity.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20would%20be%20grateful%20if%20an%20enquiry%20is%20made%20with%20respect%20to%20my%20functioning%20as%20a%20judge%20and%20what%20is%20the%20perception%20of%20the%20legal%20fraternity%20with%20regard%20to%20my%20integrity%20and%20honesty%20in%20the%20discharge%20of%20my%20judicial%20functioning%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESupreme%20Court%20Sets%20Up%20Panel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20of%20India%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20on%20Saturday%20formed%20a%20three-member%20committee%20to%20look%20into%20the%20allegations%20against%20Justice%20Varma.%20The%20committee%20members%20are%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20Court%20Chief%20Justice%20Sheel%20Nagu%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20Chief%20Justice%20GS%20Sandhawalia%20and%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%20judge%20J