ngagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdid-you-know-kader-khan-was-once-forced-to-beg-by-his-stepfather%2Farticleshow%2F119351693.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BRhea%20Chakraborty%20Went%20Through%20Untold%20Miseries%26quot%3B%3A%20Lawyer%20On%20Closure%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EActor%20Rhea%20Chakraborty's%20lawyer%20Satish%20Maneshinde%20today%20thanked%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20after%20it%20filed%20a%20closure%20report%20in%20the%20death%20case%20of%20Sushant%20Singh%20Rajput.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Maneshinde%2C%20a%20senior%20lawyer%20at%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%2C%20in%20a%20statement%20said%20the%20CBI%20has%20thoroughly%20investigated%20every%20aspect%20of%20the%20case%20from%20all%20angles%20and%20closed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20blamed%20false%20narrative%20on%20social%20media%20and%20electronic%20media%20as%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%20Rhea%20Chakraborty%20went%20through%20%26quot%3Buntold%20miseries%26quot%3B%20and%20even%20spent%2027%20days%20in%20jail%20%26quot%3Bfor%20no%20fault%20of%20hers%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20gave%20its%20findings%20before%20a%20special%20court%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20which%20will%20decide%20whether%20to%20accept%20the%20report%20or%20order%20further%20probe.%20The%20CBI%20absolved%20everyone%20-%20including%20Rhea%20Chakraborty%2C%20her%20parents%2C%20and%20brother%20-%20named%20in%20two%20first%20information%20reports%20(FIRs)%20filed%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESushant%20Singh%20Rajput%20was%20found%20dead%20in%20his%20Mumbai%20apartment%20on%20June%2014%2C%202020.%20He%20was%2034.%20The%20CBI%20took%20over%20the%20case%20from%20the%20Bihar%20Police%2C%20which%20filed%20an%20abetment%20to%20suicide%20case%20based%20on%20a%20complaint%20by%20his%20father%20in%20Patna%2C%20KK%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20conclusive%20medico-legal%20opinion%20to%20the%20CBI%2C%20forensic%20specialists%20at%20AIIMS%20dismissed%20claims%20of%20%26quot%3Bpoisoning%20and%20strangling%26quot%3B%20made%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20amount%20of%20false%20narrative%20in%20social%20media%20and%20electronic%20media%20was%20totally%20uncalled%20for.%20Due%20to%20the%20pandemic%2C%20everyone%20was%20glued%20to%20TV%20and%20social%20media%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20anything%20happening%20in%20the%20country.%20Innocent%20people%20were%20hounded%20and%20paraded%20before%20the%20media%20and%20investigative%20authorities%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Maneshinde%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20this%20does%20not%20repeat%20in%20any%20case...%20Rhea%20Chakraborty%20%5Bhad%20to%5D%20undergo%20untold%20miseries%20and%20was%20behind%20bars%20for%2027%20days%20for%20no%20fault%20of%20hers%20until%20Justice%20Sarang%20V%20Kotwal%20released%20her%20on%20bail.%20I%20salute%20her%20and%20her%20family%20for%20having%20kept%20silent%20and%20yet%20suffering%20the%20inhuman%20treatment%20they%20were%20meted%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20senior%20lawyer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20I%20must%20say%20nothing%20deterred%20us%20from%20carrying%20out%20our%20legal%20duties.%20Today%20I%20can%20share%20that%20I'm%20proud%20to%20have%20defended%20a%20fauji%20family%20pro%20bono%20and%20that%20should%20rest%20with%20the%20kind%20of%20speculative%20narration%20about%20my%20fees.%20I%20also%20thank%20a%20large%20section%20of%20the%20media%20for%20having%20supported%20me%20and%20Rhea's%20cause%20and%20her%20fight%20for%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20course%20of%20investigation%2C%20the%20CBI%20recorded%20the%20statements%20of%20Rhea%20Chakraborty%2C%20and%20others%20in%20Sushant%20Singh%20Rajput's%20close%20circle%2C%20and%20also%20collected%20the%20actor's%20medical%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20h