g%20out%20foul%20play.%20The%20report%2C%20filed%20after%20four%20and%20a%20half%20years%2C%20comes%20amidst%20a%20backdrop%20of%20intense%20media%20scrutiny%20and%20false%20narratives.%20Rhea%20Chakraborty%20and%20her%20family%20faced%20significant%20hardships%20but%20were%20ultimately%20cleared%20of%20wrongdoing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fi-salute-rhea-chakraborty-and-her-family-for-their-silent-strength-senior-advocate-satish-maneshinde-on-cbis-closure-report-in-sushant-singh-rajput-case%2Farticleshow%2F119351408.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Suicide%2C%20No%20Abetment'%3A%20CBI%20Files%20Closure%20Report%20In%20Sushant%20Rajput%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20four%20years%20after%20it%20took%20over%20the%20probe%2C%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20has%20filed%20a%20closure%20report%20in%20the%20Sushant%20Singh%20Rajput%20death%20case%2C%20sources%20said%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESushant%20Singh%20Rajput%2C%2034%2C%20was%20found%20hanging%20at%20his%20flat%20in%20Mumbai's%20Bandra%20on%20June%2014%2C%202020.%20His%20death%20had%20shocked%20thousands%20of%20fans%20and%20given%20rise%20to%20several%20theories%20-%20including%20some%20alleging%20a%20black%20magic%20angle%20-%20prompting%20an%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20the%20closure%20report%20has%20been%20filed%20in%20two%20cases%20-%20the%20allegations%20made%20by%20Sushant%20Rajput's%20father%20against%20his%20then%20girlfriend%20and%20actor%20Rhea%20Chakraborty%20and%20Ms%20Chakraborty's%20allegations%20against%20Sushant's%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20had%20taken%20over%20the%20case%20from%20the%20Bihar%20Police%20in%20August%202020.%20Sources%20said%20that%20after%20conducting%20an%20investigation%20for%20over%20four%20years%2C%20the%20agency%20did%20not%20find%20any%20evidence%20that%20anyone%20had%20driven%20Sushant%20Rajput%20to%20suicide%20and%20Ms%20Chakraborty%20and%20her%20family%20have%20been%20given%20a%20clean%20chit.%20The%20CBI%2C%20they%20said%2C%20absolved%20everyone%20named%20in%20the%20two%20FIRs%20filed%20in%20the%20case%2C%20including%20Ms%20Chakraborty%2C%20her%20parents%20and%20brother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20forensic%20team%20from%20the%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20(AIIMS)%20had%20also%20stated%20that%20Sushant%20Rajput%20was%20not%20murdered%20and%20it%20was%20a%20case%20of%20death%20by%20suicide.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAfter%20the%20death%2C%20the%20Bihar%20Police%20had%20registered%20an%20abetment%20of%20suicide%20case%20based%20on%20a%20complaint%20filed%20in%20Patna%20by%20Rajput's%20father%20KK%20Singh.%20The%20actor's%20family%20had%20accused%20Ms%20Chakraborty%20of%20mentally%20harassing%20him%2C%20medicating%20him%2C%20exploiting%20him%20for%20money%20and%20playing%20a%20role%20in%20his%20death.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnWhen%20the%20CBI%20took%20over%20the%20investigation%2C%20the%20Central%20Forensic%20Science%20Laboratory%20(CFSL)%20was%20asked%20to%20forensically%20examine%20the%20crime%20scene.%20A%20laptop%2C%20hard%20disks%2C%20a%20Canon%20camera%20and%20two%20mobiles%20were%20seized%20and%20all%20of%20them%20were%20forensically%20examined.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Chakraborty%20was%20among%20over%2020%20people%20who%20were%20questioned%20during%20the%20investigation.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAfter%20the%20submission%20of%20the%20closure%20report%2C%20the%20Bandra%20magistrate%20court%20has%20scheduled%20the%20next%20hearing%20for%20the%20case%20on%20April%208.%C2%A0%20Once%20the%20closure%20report%20is%20allowed%20by%20the%20court%2C%20the%20case%20can%20be%20disposed%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'False%20Narratives'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20Rhea%20Chakraborty's%20lawyer%20Satish%20Maneshinde%20said%20he%20and%20the%20actor%20were%20grateful%20to%20the%20CBI%20for%20having%20thoroughly%20investigated%20every%20aspect%20of%20the%20case%20but%20added%20that%20the%20false%20narratives%20around%20the%20case%20were%20%26quot%3Btotally%20uncalled%20for%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDue%20to%20the%20pandemic%20everyone%20was%20glued%20to%20the%20TV%20%26amp%3B%20social%20media%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20anything%20happening%20in%20the%20country.%20Innocent%20people%20were%20hounded%20and%20paraded%20before%20the%20media%20and%20investigative%20authorities.%20I%20hope%20this%20does%20not%20repeat%20in%20any%20case...%20Rhea%20Chakraborty%20had%20to%20undergo%20untold%20miseries%20and%20was%20behind%20bars%20for%2027%20days%20for%20no%20fault%20of%20hers%20until%20Justice%20Sarang%20V%20Kotwal%20released%20her%20on%20bail%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20salute%20her%20and%20her%20family%20for%20having%20kept%20silent%20and%20yet%20suffered%20the%20inhuman%20treatment%20they%20were%20meted%20(sic)...%20Both%20Rhea's%20family%20and%20my%20team%20and%20I%20were%20hounded%20and%20threatened...%20Today%20I%20can%20share%20that%20I'm%20proud%20to%20have%20defended%20a%20%3Cem%3Efauji%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Army)%20family%20pro%20bono...%20This%20country%20is%20still%20very%20safe%20and%20every%20citizen%20crying%20for%20justice%20has%20hope%20due%20to%20our%20vibrant%20judiciary%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawyer%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECircular%20Cancelled%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20upheld%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court's%20decision%20to%20cancel%20the%20CBI's%20lookout%20circular%20issued%20against%20them%20following%20Sushant%20Singh%20Rajput's%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20the%20petition%20%26quot%3Bfrivolous%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20bench%20of%20Justices%20BR%20Gavai%20and%20KV%20Viswanathan%20had%20observed%20that%20it%20appeared%20that%20the%20CBI%2C%20the%20government%20of%20Maharashtra%20and%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Immigration%20had%20challenged%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court's%20decision%20just%20because%20the%20accused%20were%20from%20a%20high-profile%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20warning%20you.%20You%20are%20filing%20such%20a%20frivolous%20petition%2C%20only%20because%20one%20of%20the%20accused%20is%20a%20high-profile%20person.%20It%20will%20be%20dismissed%20with%20exemplary%20cost.%20Both%20persons%20have%20deep%20roots%20in%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Gavai%20had%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20circular%20against%20Ms%20Chakraborty%2C%20her%20brother%20Showik%2C%20mother%20Sandhya%20and%20father%20Lt%20Colonel%20Indrajit%20Chakraborty%20(retired)%20were%20issued%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742666100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-08%2Fnsuonppg_sushant-singh-rajput_625x300_03_August_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcbi-files-closure-report-in-sushant-singh-rajput-death-case-7986168%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sushant%20Singh%20Rajput%20was%20found%20hanging%20at%20his%20flat%20in%20Mumbai's%20Bandra%20on%20June%2014%2C%202020.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcbi-files-closure-report-in-sushant-singh-rajput-death-case-7986168%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amanda%20Seyfried%20Says%20%E2%80%98Jennifer%E2%80%99s%20Body%E2%80%99%20Was%20a%20%E2%80%98Perfect%20Movie%E2%80%99%20Ruined%20by%20Marketing%20that%20%E2%80%98Sucked%E2%80%99%3A%20%E2%80%98The%20Marketing%20Team%20Cheapened%20It%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742665651000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FAmanda-Seyfried-Needy-Jennifers-Body-2009.png%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%