oaded%20on%20the%20website%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20in%20a%20press%20note%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20report%20submitted%20by%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20High%20Court%20of%20Delhi%2C%20response%20of%20Justice%20Yashwant%20Varma%2C%20and%20other%20documents%20are%20being%20uploaded%20on%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20website%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20top%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20of%20India%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20consulted%20collegium%20members%20Justice%20BR%20Gavai%2C%20Justice%20Surya%20Kant%2C%20Justice%20AS%20Oka%2C%20and%20Justice%20Vikram%20Nath%20on%20making%20the%20documents%20public%2C%20and%20they%20all%20agreed%20on%20it%20for%20transparency%20and%20to%20end%20misinformation%20being%20spread%20about%20the%20matter%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegation%20that%20a%20huge%20pile%20of%20cash%20was%20found%20at%20Justice%20Varma's%20house%20surfaced%20soon%20after%20a%20fire%20incident%20at%20his%20property.%20Firefighters%20reached%20there%20and%20controlled%20the%20blaze%2C%20and%20that%20was%20when%20they%20allegedly%20saw%20the%20cash%20pile.%20The%20amount%20allegedly%20discovered%20by%20the%20firefighters%20is%20not%20known.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20Khanna%20has%20also%20formed%20a%20three-member%20committee%20to%20look%20into%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20members%20are%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20Court%20Chief%20Justice%20Sheel%20Nagu%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20Chief%20Justice%20GS%20Sandhawalia%2C%20and%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%20judge%20Justice%20Anu%20Sivaraman%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20in%20a%20press%20note%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20Chief%20Justice%20for%20the%20time%20being%20has%20been%20asked%20not%20to%20assign%20any%20judicial%20work%20to%20Justice%20Varma%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20lawyer%20Harish%20Salve%2C%20who%20calls%20himself%