e%20collegium%20system%2C%20told%20NDTV%20on%20Friday%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20equipped%26quot%3B%20to%20deal%20with%20cases%20like%20the%20alleged%20recovery%20of%20a%20huge%20pile%20of%20cash%20at%20the%20home%20of%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Salve%20alleged%20the%20Delhi%20fire%20chief%20has%20said%20there%20was%20no%20recovery%20of%20cash%20from%20the%20judge's%20bungalow%2C%20giving%20rise%20to%20an%20%26quot%3Bodd%20and%20murky%26quot%3B%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20website%20shows%20Justice%20Varma%20enrolled%20as%20an%20advocate%20in%20August%201992.%20He%20was%20appointed%20additional%20judge%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20in%20October%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20took%20oath%20as%20a%20permanent%20judge%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20in%20February%202016%2C%20before%20being%20appointed%20a%20judge%20of%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20in%20October%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20currently%20heading%20a%20division%20bench%2C%20dealing%20with%20cases%20of%20sales%20tax%2C%20goods%20and%20services%20tax%2C%20company%20appeals%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20to%20transfer%20Justice%20Varma%20was%20unrelated%20to%20the%20inquiry%20into%20the%20cash%20stash%20case%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20on%20Friday.%20The%20top%20court%20flagged%20%26quot%3Bmisinformation%20and%20rumours%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20reasons%20why%20Justice%20Varma's%20transfer%20to%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20was%20linked%20to%20the%20cash%20recovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742659320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Ff4aj2l1_delhi-high-court-judge-justice-yashwant-varma_625x300_21_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftop-court-sets-up-panel-to-probe-allegations-against-judge-yashwant-varma-in-cash-pile-case-7985829%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20has%20for