Fstory%2Famp%2Fdetained-istanbul-mayor-ekrem-imamoglu-faces-second-day-of-questioning-as-protests-intensify-13333798%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Columbia%20University%20Agreed%20To%20Do%20For%20%24400m%20From%20Trump%20Administration%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EColumbia%20University%20has%20given%20in%20to%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20demands%2C%20agreeing%20to%20implement%20significant%20changes%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20reinstatement%20of%20%24400%20million%20in%20federal%20funding.%20The%20university's%20decision%20comes%20after%20the%20government%20pulled%20its%20funding%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20citing%20allegations%20of%20antisemitism%20on%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20agreement%2C%20Columbia%20has%20agreed%20to%20ban%20face%20masks%20on%20campus%2C%20empower%20security%20officers%20to%20remove%20or%20arrest%20individuals%2C%20and%20place%20its%20Middle%20Eastern%2C%20South%20Asian%20and%20African%20Studies%20department%20under%20a%20new%20official.%20This%20move%20has%20been%20met%20with%20criticism%20from%20professors%20and%20academics%2C%20who%20worry%20that%20it%20sets%20a%20dangerous%20precedent%20for%20government%20control%20over%20academic%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20has%20been%20cracking%20down%20on%20universities%2C%20warning%20at%20least%2060%20institutions%20of%20possible%20action%20over%20alleged%20failure%20to%20comply%20with%20federal%20civil%20rights%20laws%20related%20to%20antisemitism.%20The%20administration%20has%20also%20targeted%20law%20firms%20that%20it%20claims%20have%20helped%20Trump's%20political%20opponents%20or%20prosecuted%20him%20unfairly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EColumbia's%20agreement%20has%20been%20met%20with%20disappointment%20from%20some%20quarters%2C%20with%20Professor%20Jonathan%20Zimmerman%2C%20an%20education%20historian%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bsad%20day%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20university.%20